# Project: Solana Sniper Bot
A memecoin trading bot for Solana blockchain using Jupiter API for swaps.

# Code Style
- Use ES6+ features
- Clear, descriptive variable names
- Comprehensive error handling
- Async/await for promises
- Comments for complex logic
- ESLint standard config

# Architecture
- Modular design with separate services
- Environment variables for config
- Centralized logging
- Service-based architecture

# Key Files
/src
 /config - Network configs
 /services - Core bot services
 /utils - Helper functions
 /index.js - Entry point

# Dependencies  
- @solana/web3.js: Core Solana functionality
- @solana/spl-token: Token operations
- dotenv: Environment management

# Testing
- Unit tests for core logic
- Integration tests for services
- Test on devnet first
- Monitor for edge cases

# Security 
- Never commit private keys
- Validate all inputs
- Rate limiting
- Error recovery